                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">PAY ESTIMATE CONFIGURATIONS</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                              <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Default Retention Percentage</uicontrol>
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Enter the retention percentage for pay estimates.

</p>
                              <p class="- topic/p ">The retention percentage of all pay estimates of all contracts that are created is set to this defined percentage value.</p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">FINAL PAY ESTIMATE CONFIGURATIONS

</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                              <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Required Validation</uicontrol>
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Select the check box to enforce the corresponding validation when generating the final pay estimate of a contract. 

These validations are enforced for all new contracts that are created.</p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
